Summary: woke up 3am seen object shape like rectangler shape white above the rocky mtn in July 2010 lasting approx 2 mins
divs: Sighting DetailsI was camping in colorado mtns in 7-20-2010 woke up around 3am to see an object white in color, like the moon at nite, rectangler in shape like a stick of gum moving in a stright line im not sure of the direction. This could have been the spacelab maybe I have been looking on the web never seen anything like it.
